51:["$","p","88",{"className":"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4","children":"Set realistic expectations: Your GPS tracker is accurate to about ±30-50 feet in normal conditions. Use geofences (large virtual boundaries) rather than expecting exact position. This gives you peace of mind without frustration over imprecision."}]
